#if soper
Command provided by: nickserv/set_accountname
#endif
Help for SET ACCOUNTNAME:

SET ACCOUNTNAME allows you to change your account
name to any nick registered to your account.
Your account name is used in various places as
a name for you.

Note: You may be restricted in how often you may
change your account name.  If you aren't yet eligible
to change your account name, you will receive an error
message that will tell you how much longer you must wait.

Syntax: SET ACCOUNTNAME <nick>
